\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

) that satisfies the properties described in the statement of the theorem.
 To see this, we first have to show that the functional defined above indeed
 satisfes the three requisite properties and then show that it is the only
 such functional.
 Before we do this, note that the set 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \bar{\mu}_{0}\left(s\right)\mid s\in\mathcal{M}_{\textnormal{sim}}\left(\X,\F\right)\text{s.t\ }s\leq f\right\} $
\end_inset

