\begin_inset Formula $A_{n}=\left\{ x\in\X\mid f_{n}\left(x\right)\geq ts\left(x\right)\right\} $
\end_inset

.
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{n}\leq f_{n+1}$
\end_inset

, we have that 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{n}\subseteq A_{n+1}$
\end_inset

.
 Moreover, for any 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\X$
\end_inset

