\begin_inset Formula $\indicate_{A}\stackrel{\mu-\text{a.e}}{=}\indicate_{B}$
\end_inset

.
 This is easily shown in the following result.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proposition
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "prop:almostEverywhereEqualSets"

\end_inset

Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\measurespace$
\end_inset

 be a measure space.
 For any 
\begin_inset Formula $A,B\in\F$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A\stackrel{\mu-\text{a.e}}{=}B$
\end_inset

